<p>would become soon a very valuable country if all the arabs were hunted out of it &amp; the Jews settled here. After what I have seen I am all in favour of letting the Jews have the place. Perfect little paradises they create for themselves.</p>
<p>Ayunkara  29th Nov [1917]<br/>We left Sidret el Hareriyeh on the 27th &amp; came up here in one day. There is quite a big war on here now. The turks seem to be making their first stand here on a line roughly Jaffa-Jerusalem.</p>
